text: Cessières-Suzy is a new commune in the department of Aisne in the Hauts-de- France region in north France. It was created on 1 January 2019 and is made of the former communes of Cessières and Suzy.Arrêté préfectoral 11 December 2018 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Aisne
title: Cessières-Suzy
